      <h1 class="h4 mb-3">6. Replace related content outside the target with <code>het-also</code></h1>
      <div class="tutorial-content mb-4">
        <p>Use <code>het-also</code> when one response should update the target pane and one or more elements elsewhere on the page.</p>
        <p>Each listed id must exist both in the current document and in the response. <code>het-also</code> only applies to elements outside the target pane.</p>
        <p>On submit buttons, <code>het-also=&quot;&quot;</code> clears a form-level <code>het-also</code>.</p>
        <p>Relevant reference:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="reference/requests#additional-replacements-with-het-also">Additional replacements with <code>het-also</code></a></li>
          <li><a href="reference/errors#het-also"><code>het-also</code> errors</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

